text: Ahmet Oğuz (born 16 January 1993) is a Turkish professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for Kasımpaşa. ==Career== ===Club career=== Ahmet Oğuz began his professional career at Gençlerbirliği. ==International career== Ahmet Oğuz was called up to the Turkey national football team for World Cup qualifiers against Croatia on September 2016. ==References== ==External links== *Soccerway Profile Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:People from Sorgun, Yozgat Category:Turkish footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:Gençlerbirliği S.K. footballers Category:Hacettepe S.K. footballers Category:Süper Lig players
